snippet.textDisplay: Pakistan's Coke Studio is so consistently good! Everything is just about perfect - choice of singers, instruments, music, and type of performance. The studio is stylish. India's coke studio is a mixed bag - some pieces are very good and others so-so. We try to be a bit too adventurous, and if it does not work - then it does not work big-time. Still nice to switch from one to the other, but I personally am heavily aligned to Pakistan's version.
snippet.textOriginal: Pakistan's Coke Studio is so consistently good! Everything is just about perfect - choice of singers, instruments, music, and type of performance. The studio is stylish. India's coke studio is a mixed bag - some pieces are very good and others so-so. We try to be a bit too adventurous, and if it does not work - then it does not work big-time. Still nice to switch from one to the other, but I personally am heavily aligned to Pakistan's version.
